{"tid":2393413,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"緬甸警方指昂山素姬非法進口對講機　拘留她至本月中","createTime":"2021-02-03T12:08:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-04T00:58:43.000Z","uid":240362,"like":22,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"33fc0de15b15012d1a3ec979610f56a3e2243324","tid":2393413,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T12:08:12.000Z","msg":"緬甸警方起訴國務資政昂山素姬違反出入口法例，要求將她拘留至本月15日。<br />\n<br />\n警方搜查昂山素姬的住所，發現非法進口對講機，懷疑她未經批准非法使用。<br />\n<br />\n緬甸軍方接管權力後改組政府，並舉行首次政府會議，國防軍總司令敏昂萊強調，接掌政權是無可避免。<br />\n<br />\n而全國70多間醫院員工發起罷工抗議，有民眾響應號召，晚上敲打爐具器皿表達不滿。<br />\n<br />\n聯合國安理會在中國反對下，未能就發出譴責聲明達成一致。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1573905-20210203.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1573905-20210203.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=f02Xtm2mX5FaAGCExHUdjSC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=f73cefe6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1573905-20210203.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=90473c0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1573905-20210203.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"ab12f13b73d074741170865ac27896a6c2c383f3","tid":2393413,"uid":77717,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T12:09:56.000Z","msg":"同支那一樣，求其搵啲嘢屈你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"430f7c5de92eab8ae8012dd8b0aeb49144d3d8e8","tid":2393413,"uid":51271,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T12:10:02.000Z","msg":"同港共一樣"},{"pid":"886ae73eed25bbeca6fe9bfe2fbdc3226b08e5c1","tid":2393413,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T12:11:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr